<hr style="width: 100%; height: 2px;"><small><font
 style="font-family: Verdana;" color="#0000af" size="+1"><small><b>Bio
sketch</b></small></font></small>
<blockquote style="font-family: Verdana;"><small>I
received the Ph.D.
in Control Engineering in 1992 from the University of Rome "La
Sapienza". In 1990-1991 I was Visiting Scholar at the Center for
Robotic Systems of the University of California at Santa Barbara. In
1993 I joined the <a href="http://www.dis.uniroma1.it">Dipartimento
di
Informatica e Sistemistica</a> (DIS)
of the University of Rome "La
Sapienza", where I currently am an Associate Professor of Automatic
Control. I have also held adjoint teaching positions at various italian
universities, including the University of Siena in 1992-93, the
University of Cassino in 1997-98 and the University of Roma Tre since
2002. </small>
  <p><small>I
am a member of the DIS <a href="../../index.html">Robotics
Laboratory</a> and an Associate
Editor of the <a href="http://www.dis.uniroma1.it/%7Eieeetro/">IEEE
Transactions on
Robotics</a>.</small></p>
</blockquote>
